    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310730/extras/c44cd10ba0019805745ba1c1b09f0fc4.poster.avif?t=1757646509\" width=600 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310730/extras/c44cd10ba0019805745ba1c1b09f0fc4.webm?t=1757646509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310730/extras/c44cd10ba0019805745ba1c1b09f0fc4.mp4?t=1757646509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>故事开始于一场无情的祝融，烧毁了正在举办的中秋祭祀。<br>导致魑魅魍魉跑到天界与凡间肆虐。<br><br>为了重启仪式，主角「红娘」必需协助父母，到镇上采购祭祀需要的食材。<br>并在两只神兽「饕餮」与「负屭」的协助下完成任务；<br>阻止捣乱祭祀的不速之客，让天界与凡间重回秩序。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><i></i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310730/extras/4f8f4e95d62ba93e75fb617f6576ddd4.poster.avif?t=1757646509\" width=600 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310730/extras/4f8f4e95d62ba93e75fb617f6576ddd4.webm?t=1757646509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310730/extras/4f8f4e95d62ba93e75fb617f6576ddd4.mp4?t=1757646509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>中式风格的美术与建筑场景</li></ul></strong>无论是华丽的九歌食府或是充满特色的城镇，每张地图都值得您慢慢去探索和品味。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310730/extras/3a29bb6ee299027100a3f93524b64daa.poster.avif?t=1757646509\" width=600 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310730/extras/3a29bb6ee299027100a3f93524b64daa.webm?t=1757646509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>皮影戏故事与真实食谱</li></ul></strong>用纸雕皮影戏呈现的传说故事，实际制作拍摄的月饼食谱，让您在游戏里有更多的沉浸感与惊喜！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310730/extras/0ffb594a543606d8ad5e26e881bcdd67.poster.avif?t=1757646509\" width=600 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310730/extras/0ffb594a543606d8ad5e26e881bcdd67.webm?t=1757646509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310730/extras/0ffb594a543606d8ad5e26e881bcdd67.mp4?t=1757646509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>两种战斗模式与四种难度选择</li></ul></strong>不同的选择，会影响到战斗玩法；我们提供三种难度和无战斗版本，让您自由选择。<br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>以诙谐喜剧改编中国神话故事</li></ul></strong>搞笑有趣的剧情，打破对神话故事的既定印象！适合喜爱轻松欢乐剧情的玩家。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特别感谢</h2>协助游戏上架steam：<br>Maker製造機- Chimaki<br><br>多语言系统插件：<br>Mirai<br><br>宣传片BGM：<br>魔王魂",
